      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1901_AS_RBH_2_00016"/>Herrn Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Rich. Beer
                     Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb44278" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Pörtschach</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1110" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Villa Arnstein</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p><pb facs="1901_AS_RBH_2_00017"/><hi rend="pre-print">Gruss aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb946">Vahrn</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1901_AS_RBH_2_00017"/>Vielen Dank für den Brief. Antwort demnäch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t.</p><p>Hier i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t es hei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s – aber warm!<note xml:id="FN1901-07-17-1" type="footnote"><p>Es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ogar kühl.</p></note> Ihr Andenken lebt fort, wie das der Ihren.</p><closer>Herzlichst Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
